    <title>Blog Starter</title>
    <link href="/2023/08/30/blog-starter/"/>
    <url>/2023/08/30/blog-starter/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="blog-with-Hexo"><a href="#blog-with-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="blog with Hexo"></a>blog with Hexo</h2><h3 id="installation-and-setup"><a href="#installation-and-setup" class="headerlink" title="installation and setup"></a>installation and setup</h3><blockquote><p>ref: <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/num_001/article/details/126370104">https://blog.csdn.net/num_001/article/details/126370104</a></p><p><a href="http://www.taodudu.cc/news/show-5247386.html?action=onClick">http://www.taodudu.cc/news/show-5247386.html?action=onClick</a></p></blockquote><h4 id="install-NodeJS"><a href="#install-NodeJS" class="headerlink" title="install NodeJS"></a>install NodeJS</h4><p>choose a early LTS version of nodejs: <a href="https://nodejs.org/download/release/v14.21.3/">https://nodejs.org/download/release/v14.21.3/</a></p><p>move to somewhere for applications like: &#x2F;usr&#x2F;opt and link it to &#x2F;usr&#x2F;bin as:</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">sudo <span class="hljs-built_in">ln</span> -s /usr/local/node-v8.9.3-linux-x64/bin/node /usr/local/bin/node <br>sudo <span class="hljs-built_in">ln</span> -s /usr/local/node-v8.9.3-linux-x64/bin/npm  /usr/local/bin/npm<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># test if success</span><br>npm -v<br>node -v<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>then we have <code>npm</code> and <code>node</code></p><h4 id="install-hexo-using-npm"><a href="#install-hexo-using-npm" class="headerlink" title="install hexo using npm"></a>install hexo using npm</h4><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">npm install -g hexo-cli --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># test</span><br>hexo<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># link hexo if test failed</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">ln</span> -s /usr/local/node-v8.9.3-linux-x64/lib/node_modules/hexo-cli/bin/hexo /usr/bin/hexo<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>now we have <code>hexo</code></p><h3 id="create-hexo-blog-website-with-local-directory"><a href="#create-hexo-blog-website-with-local-directory" class="headerlink" title="create hexo blog website with local directory"></a>create hexo blog website with local directory</h3><blockquote><p>see ref: <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/github-pages.html#%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/github-pages.html#%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2</a></p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># create a desired folder at proper place and do initiation</span></span><br>mkdir blog_hexo<br>cd blog_hexo<br>hexo init<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">change npm <span class="hljs-built_in">source</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> initiation failed</span><br>npm config set registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># start server and visit it via local port</span></span><br>hexo server<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>then we can start edit blog using <code>hexo</code></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># github deployer</span></span><br>npm install hexo-deployer-git --save<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>in file <code>_config.yml</code>, change <code>deploy</code> part as:</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">deploy:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">git</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">repository:</span> <span class="hljs-string">https://github.com/&lt;username&gt;/&lt;project&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment"># example, https://github.com/hexojs/hexojs.github.io</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment"># git@github.com:hexojs/hexojs.github.io.git</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">branch:</span> <span class="hljs-string">master</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>Note:  github now only supports key login, so generate your local ssh&#x2F;gpg key and use ssh repo address like: <a href="mailto:&#x67;&#x69;&#116;&#64;&#x67;&#x69;&#x74;&#x68;&#117;&#x62;&#x2e;&#99;&#111;&#x6d;">&#x67;&#x69;&#116;&#64;&#x67;&#x69;&#x74;&#x68;&#117;&#x62;&#x2e;&#99;&#111;&#x6d;</a>:hexojs&#x2F;hexojs.github.io.git</strong></p><p><code>Tips:</code> seems github.io only supports lower-case url</p><h3 id="blog-finetune"><a href="#blog-finetune" class="headerlink" title="blog finetune"></a>blog finetune</h3><p>theme here is using <a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid</a>, with its <a href="https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/start/">start-up manual</a></p><ul><li><p>abstract</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">contetns as abstract<br>&lt;!-- more --&gt;<br>contents left<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>Front-matter settings of single article</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html">---<br>title: title<br>author: author<br>tags: [tag1, tag2] # tags<br>index_img: /img/img.jpg # cover image in /source/img/example.jpg or url<br>banner_img: /img/post_banner.jpg # article specific banner<br>banner_img_height: 60<br>banner_mask_alpha: 0.5<br>date: YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS # time<br>excerpt: abstract # abstract content<br>hide: true # if private article<br>sticky: 100 # if stick at top, bigger toppercomment: &#x27;valine&#x27; # whether to use comments<br>math: true # if needs formula showup<br>layout: about # page layout<br>---<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>generating new custom page:</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">hexo new page customPageName<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>then edit <code>/source/customPageName/index.md</code></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html"># if need markdown<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span> <span class="hljs-attr">class</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;markdown-body&quot;</span>&gt;</span>contents<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">div</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="Blog-post"><a href="#Blog-post" class="headerlink" title="Blog post"></a>Blog post</h3><p>generate new post</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">hexo new <span class="hljs-string">&quot;customPage&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>modify <code>/source/_post/customPage.md</code></p><p>and deploy</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh"><span class="hljs-comment"># generate blog</span><br>hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy<br><span class="hljs-comment"># see the outcome immediately on local host</span><br>hexo server<br><span class="hljs-comment"># or shorter</span><br>hexo s<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Fluid-cheatsheet"><a href="#Fluid-cheatsheet" class="headerlink" title="Fluid cheatsheet"></a>Fluid cheatsheet</h3><blockquote><p>code language below is misused intentionally to display source code, all codes are for post main body in markdown</p></blockquote><h4 id="Post-Font"><a href="#Post-Font" class="headerlink" title="Post Font"></a>Post Font</h4><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-section"># front setup</span><br><span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br>  /* whole page font <span class="hljs-emphasis">*/</span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis">  html, body, .markdown-body &#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis">    font-family: KaiTi,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Georgia, sans, serif;</span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis">    font-size: 15px;</span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis">  &#125;</span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis"></span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis">  /*</span> markdwon font only <span class="hljs-emphasis">*/</span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis">  .markdown-body &#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis">    font-family: KaiTi,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Georgia, sans, serif;</span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis">    font-size: 15px;</span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis">  &#125;</span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis"><span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">style</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis"></span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis">contents</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="note"><a href="#note" class="headerlink" title="note"></a>note</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">&#123;% note noteName %&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment"># noteName: primary, secondary, success, danger, warning, info, light</span><br>note content<br>&#123;% endnote %&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="in-line-label"><a href="#in-line-label" class="headerlink" title="in-line label"></a>in-line label</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">&#123;% label labelname @text %&#125; <br><span class="hljs-comment"># labelName: primary default info success warning danger</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="checkbox"><a href="#checkbox" class="headerlink" title="checkbox"></a>checkbox</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">&#123;% cb text, checked?, incline? %&#125; <br><span class="hljs-comment"># e.g. &#123;% cb text, true, true %&#125;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># ?: false or true, incline for whether break lines</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="button"><a href="#button" class="headerlink" title="button"></a>button</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">&#123;% btn url, text, title %&#125; <br><span class="hljs-comment"># url: link url, text: text shown in button, title: text shown on mouseover</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="graph-set"><a href="#graph-set" class="headerlink" title="graph set"></a>graph set</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">&#123;% gi total n1-n2-... %&#125; <span class="hljs-comment"># total: total graph number, n1...: graph each line</span><br>![](url)...<br>&#123;% endgi%&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="footer"><a href="#footer" class="headerlink" title="footer"></a>footer</h4><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">a line need footer[^1]<br><br>[<span class="hljs-symbol">^1</span>]:<span class="hljs-link">footer 1</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
